\p{B. Victor and L. Iannini. \em{The Communal Science Lab}. Dynamicland Foundation, 2024. Identifies four values systematically absent from computing: visibility, agency, physical reality, in-person collaboration. The BCI Factory manifesto ([[bcf-0002]]) is a direct instantiation of all four.}
